# Human Supreme Authority

- The Human Supreme is the only role that approves merging integrated work to protected branches when this package is in effect.
- Agents propose changes and evidence; they do not override human merge decisions.
- If instructions conflict with repository governance or safety, stop and ask the Human Supreme.
